sequenceDiagram

  participant ING as Ingestion client (sensors)

  participant API as API: prediction service

  participant MODEL as ML runtime

  participant CALLER as Response consumer



  ING->>API: POST /score

  API->>MODEL: features

  MODEL-->>API: score and flag

  API-->>ING: 200 JSON with score and flag



  CALLER->>API: GET /status

  API-->>CALLER: status {"service": ..., "model_loaded": true}



  CALLER->>API: GET /recent_scores

  API-->>CALLER: JSON list of recent predictions
